stepText1 = Let's go through an example...<BR>We have selected <font color="yellow">BRO</font> You can quickly browse
raw data by Vendor, Technology or Source Type.  Once we select a <font color="yellow">Vendor</font>, the rest of the f
ields update as well as the list of searched sourcetypes update.
stepText2 = So, here we get a list of <font color="yellow">BRO</font> data sourcetypes for you to further drill down.<
BR> You can quickly dive into a type of source type you want to either demo and learn.
tourPage = datalab_01
type = interactive
urlData = ?form.VENDOR=BRO&form.TECH=Network&form.SOURCETYPE=*&earliest=0&latest=


