stepText1 = Now this is Splunk free search interface, if you drill further down from the expanded events.
stepText2 = The data source you are looking for is entered here as search conditions.
tourPage = search
type = interactive
urlData = ?earliest=0&latest=&sid=demo_owner_ZGVtb19vd25lcg__datalab__search5_1464361609.1756&q=search%20sourcetype%3D
bro_dns%20%7C%20head%202000&display.page.search.mode=fast&dispatch.sample_ratio=1


